     "color": "rgb(223,244,193)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 6000,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 8880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Delete the error storage.",
     "color": "rgb(223,244,193)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 6840,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "After that you can switch ignition ON again.",
     "color": "rgb(223,244,193)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 6480,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "After that a part of the clutch system is substituted and once all the operations above described have been terminated, it is highly recommended to make a short test drive, in order the permit the self teaching of some clutch parameters.",
